item.title: Imperial Tae Kwon Do take on Italy
item.author: Maija-lisa Han,
item.description: Last weekend, six students from the Imperial College Union Tae Kwon Do club (ICUTKD) travelled to Cagliari in Italy where they competed in the 4th International Mediterranean Open.
